    "body": "A couple of things here:\r\n\r\n- This seems to be a solidity-coverage and/or hardhat-preprocessor issue, but both of those plugins are community plugins. This issue tracker is used for Hardhat itself and our official plugins.\r\n- Are you using preprocessor to be able to use Hardhat with Foundry? If that's the case, take a look at [our guide](https://hardhat.org/hardhat-runner/docs/advanced/hardhat-and-foundry) on how to use both tools together.\r\n\r\nTentatively closing, I'll re-open if this turns out to be a problem in Hardhat itself, but seems unlikely.",
